    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320440/extras/4f34d5538a51fdf703aabbfc93c2c9a0.avif?t=1756838127\" width=616 height=175 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好在CannonHead中踏上史诗般的冒险吧！这是一款第三人称射击游戏，平衡了激烈的战斗和身临其境的探索。灵感来自于20世纪20年代和30年代的儿童动画，CannonHead采用了将2D动画的复古效果转化为3D环境的技术，保留了经典的魅力和怀旧的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索各种独特的世界和环境，招募有价值的同伴，发现新的武器和装备来帮助你面对越来越强大的敌人。所有这些都在试图逃离对你独特辞职方式不满的前老板的追捕中进行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入这次精彩的旅程，看看你是否有能力克服挑战并保护你的盟友！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320440/extras/1e3f7947c9ba61dc43f76cff0fd4abf9.poster.avif?t=1756838127\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320440/extras/1e3f7947c9ba61dc43f76cff0fd4abf9.webm?t=1756838127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320440/extras/1e3f7947c9ba61dc43f76cff0fd4abf9.mp4?t=1756838127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特点</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>平衡的战斗与探索:</strong> 集热血动作和沉浸式探索于一体。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的视觉风格: </strong>创新技术将20年代和30年代动画的魅力带入3D世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样化的世界和环境: </strong>旅行穿越各种独特且精彩的场景。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>旅程同伴: </strong>招募盟友来帮助你完成任务。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样化的武器库: </strong>寻找并利用多种武器和装备。</p></li></ul>",
